CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 13, 1959, pg. A16 reads: "Guest Model - Alberta Thompson, another guest model for the D.I.'s shows a lounging outfit featuring knit trousers and a print top."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Alberta Thompson wearing dark pants, belt, and floral button down shirt with flipped up collar and three quarter length sleeves, kneeling next to potted plant in Gloria Grate's home, preparing for the D.I.'s "Atlantic City U.S.A." revue held at the Press Club in the Hotel Sherwyn
